      <title>报告称 2024 年英国女性商界领袖数量将下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/number-female-business-leaders-britain-falls-2024-report-says-2024-10-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家咨询公司周四表示，英国企业中担任高管的女性数量八年来首次下降，这种“令人无法接受”的逆转可能会导致性别平等再推迟五代。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/number-female-business-leaders-britain-falls-2024-report-says-2024-10-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 23:02:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于经济停滞，欧洲央行将连续第二次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-set-second-straight-rate-cut-economy-stagnates-2024-10-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行很可能于周四再次降息，理由是欧元区通胀目前逐渐得到控制，而经济则陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-set-second-straight-rate-cut-economy-stagnates-2024-10-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 22:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Discover Financial 季度利润因利息收入强劲和拨备减少而跃升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/discover-financial-quarterly-profit-jumps-robust-interest-income-lower-2024-10-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该公司周三表示，Discover Financial 第三季度利润跃升 43%，原因是这家美国信用卡发行商的净利息收入增加，且潜在不良贷款拨备减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/discover-financial-quarterly-profit-jumps-robust-interest-income-lower-2024-10-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 21:08:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，麦肯锡即将解决美国阿片类药物调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/mckinsey-nears-500-mln-settlement-with-doj-over-opioid-probe-bloomberg-news-2024-10-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位知情人士透露，咨询公司麦肯锡公司即将与美国检察官达成协议，将支付逾 5 亿美元，以解决长期以来联邦调查，该调查针对该公司过去帮助阿片类药物制造商提高销量的行为，据称此举导致了致命的成瘾流行病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/mckinsey-nears-500-mln-settlement-with-doj-over-opioid-probe-bloomberg-news-2024-10-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 18:50:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，裕信银行因欧洲央行对俄罗斯的要求而陷入法庭僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-court-limbo-over-ecbs-russia-demands-sources-say-2024-10-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士向路透社透露，裕信银行仍在等待法院裁决，以确定其是否必须立即减少在俄罗斯的业务，以遵守欧洲央行的命令。几个月前，裕信银行曾提出异议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-court-limbo-over-ecbs-russia-demands-sources-say-2024-10-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 17:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
